      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published best-practice guidance for rotary blood pump CFD. Giersiepen hemolysis power-law correlation adopted per FDA hemolysis guidance. Formal model-form uncertainty analysis not required at MRL 2 and is scoped out."
