      "rationale": "Blood density set to 1056 kg/m³ (±5 kg/m³, literature range). Dynamic viscosity modeled as 0.0035 Pa·s with ±8% aleatory variability based on published donor population data. Inlet velocity profiles derived from Womersley solution for pulsatile CPB flow waveform. Input uncertainty bounds propagated via Monte Carlo sampling (500 runs) to produce RH distribution. UQ report UQ-CPB-2024-01 documents input characterization. A note in the report states that a follow-on sensitivity analysis is planned to identify which input parameters contribute most to RH variance, but this analysis has not yet been performed."
