    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out under the MRL 2 credibility plan. Uncertainty quantification has been completed, with Monte Carlo propagation demonstrating that the 95th-percentile RH remains below 0.92 across all five operating conditions, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion with margin. The UQ report notes that sensitivity analysis to rank dominant input drivers is planned for a future revision; the assessment team accepted this deferral given the available UQ results and validation evidence. The overall credibility package is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
